# Frontend Skill Routing

- For frontend tasks in this repository, use the project skill at `.cursor/skills/frontend-development/SKILL.md`.
- Treat this skill as the default workflow for React component edits, CSS/layout changes, and UI interaction updates.
- Validate user-facing changes with browser automation and capture at least one snapshot plus one screenshot.
